features: NATURAL INGREDIENTS: Our repellent is friendly to environment , contains blend of effective essential oils that stop deer browsing by using multiple smell. This animal repellent will keep deer, elk, and moose out of your garden and yard. Proven effective protect your garden and plants for up to 60 days.
STRONG REPELLER : This unique blend of ingredients will mess up with animal's' senses, making them panic and will repel them immediately.

LONG LASTING PROTECTION, RAIN-RESISTANT: Specifically designed to repel deers outdoors, the deer repellent delivers a long lasting scent. Thousands of experiments have shown great irritation to deers, more effective than any other deer repellent product. Long lasting protection to your family.Water resistant, no need to be re-applied after rainfall.

NO MESS, EASY TO USE: It work immediately when you hang or place the deer repellent near the plants, flowers or trees that you want to protect, creat an effective deer control barrier to get rid of deers and rabbits from garden, bushes, low-growing flower beds, landscaped, vegetable garden, yard, shrubs, trees and vines etc.

PET & PLANT SAFE - All natural ingredients safe for people, pets, fruits, vegetables when used as directed. Made of exclusive formula. Full refund if the repellents don't work. Perfect for lawns, flowerbeds, fruit and vegetable gardens, garbage cans, garages, sheds, barns and so on.
